# ── Agent / dev artifacts ──
# CR-2026-07-03 — memory/ and memory_repo/ hold the project's change-request
# registry, intake docs, and control dashboard. They MUST be tracked in git
# so the operating prompt at memory/control/ and the CR history under
# memory/change_requests/ are shared across contributors, not stashed on
# individual containers. memory/test_credentials.md stays ignored (line 79).
test_reports/
test_result.md
frontend/src/__tests__/
backend/tests/

# ── Platform config ──
.emergent/

# ── Root docs ──
# Match only the top-level README.md, not READMEs nested anywhere
# (e.g. memory/change_requests/README.md must stay tracked).
/README.md

